00:17:05,875 --> 00:17:08,791
[KURONO]
This... fucker... is... toast!

256
00:17:12,791 --> 00:17:14,458
[ALL gasp]

257
00:17:19,333 --> 00:17:22,375
[yells]

258
00:17:31,125 --> 00:17:33,416
What just happened?

259
00:17:46,083 --> 00:17:48,625
[ALL gasp, murmur]

260
00:17:55,041 --> 00:17:57,791
[ALL gasp, scream]

261
00:18:37,208 --> 00:18:41,125
[KONTA]
Fuck... Is it dead?

262
00:18:41,208 --> 00:18:43,541
[TOMAO]
Well, it looks dead, but...

263
00:18:43,625 --> 00:18:46,833
What do you think happened to
that crazy son of a bitch?

264
00:18:48,500 --> 00:18:50,375
--[ALL scream]
--[JJ] Oh, my god!

265
00:18:50,458 --> 00:18:55,666
[KURONO panting]

266
00:18:55,750 --> 00:18:57,958
[KATO]
Kei? Are you...

267
00:19:22,791 --> 00:19:23,791
[gasps]

268
00:19:26,250 --> 00:19:27,625
Promise me something.

269
00:19:27,708 --> 00:19:30,666
Promise we'll still take
that drive together.

270
00:19:31,708 --> 00:19:35,708
[KURONO]
Don't worry. I'm not gonna die.

271
00:19:40,208 --> 00:19:42,083
[KISHIMOTO]
She's right, you know.

272
00:19:43,583 --> 00:19:46,291
As long as you and
Kurono are with us...

273
00:19:46,375 --> 00:19:48,125
...we'll make it back.

274
00:19:51,125 --> 00:19:52,333
[HOJO gasps]

275
00:19:53,375 --> 00:19:55,208
There's still two
more of them left!

276
00:19:55,291 --> 00:19:56,750
[ALL gasp, chatter]

277
00:19:56,833 --> 00:19:58,625
How much time is left?

278
00:19:58,708 --> 00:20:01,250
There's just over a
half hour remaining.

279
00:20:03,041 --> 00:20:05,000
Only 30 minutes left, huh?

280
00:20:08,250 --> 00:20:11,208
But as long as they're
the small ones, we're good.

281
00:20:11,291 --> 00:20:14,541
Right! We'll split
into two groups!

282
00:20:14,625 --> 00:20:16,833
Choose your side.
Go with him or with me!

283
00:20:16,916 --> 00:20:18,083
[HOJO]
Huh?!

284
00:20:18,166 --> 00:20:20,708
You want me to be a team
leader?! Are you nuts?!

285
00:20:20,791 --> 00:20:24,291
We're all depending
on you. You can do it.

286
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:30,625
Listen up! The next thirty
minutes will decide everything!

287
00:20:30,708 --> 00:20:34,916
Who's gonna win... us or them!

288
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:39,000
Whatever happens next, we've
come too far to turn back now.

289
00:20:58,708 --> 00:21:00,083
[KATO]
Remember:

290
00:21:00,166 --> 00:21:03,208
The Gantz always attacks us
in ways we can't predict.

291
00:21:03,291 --> 00:21:05,833
Therefore, we have to
fight all of its attacks.

292
00:21:05,916 --> 00:21:09,291
Eliminate every adversary
it puts in front of us.

293
00:21:09,375 --> 00:21:12,750
That's the only way
we'll be able to survive.

294
00:22:46,125 --> 00:22:48,125
[KISHIMOTO]
I've made it this far.

295
00:22:48,208 --> 00:22:52,125
A lot of things have happened,
but I've been able to survive.

296
00:22:52,208 --> 00:22:55,083
But now...

297
00:22:55,166 --> 00:22:59,958
Next episode, "Just Shoot Me."

